'''DVD播放器'''（{{lang-en|DVD Player}}，也称为dvdplay.exe）是一个包含在[[Windows_98|Windows 98]]、[[Windows_Me|Windows Me]]和[[Windows_2000|Windows 2000]]中的[[计算机程序|计算机程序]]，用来自动播放[[DVD|DVD]][[光盘|光盘]]。DVD播放器从Windows 98开始引入，并在之后的[[Windows_XP|Windows XP]]开始被移除。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://technet.microsoft.com/library/cc768182.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396|title=Chapter 12 - Multimedia|accessdate=30 July 2015|date=|last=|first=|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|website=[[Microsoft_TechNet|TechNet]]|archive-date=2016-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617105034/https://technet.microsoft.com/library/cc768182.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396}}</ref>从Windows XP开始，DVD播放采用内置的其他应用程序，例如[[Windows_Media_Player|Windows Media Player]]和[[Windows_Media_Center|Windows Media Center]]。

由于Media Center从[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]开始被移除，并且DVD编解码器也已在此前从Windows操作系统中移除，一个新的独立的DVD播放器程序被再次引入。

== 功能 ==
在DVD播放器启动时，它会按字母顺序从C:开始搜索所有本地驱动器，寻找一个Video_TS文件夹。找到此文件夹后，将会加载里面的数据文件并开始播放视频流。如果在查找DVD驱动器前找到了该文件夹，播放器将尝试播放首个找到的文件夹中的数据。

== 兼容性 ==
在Windows 98和Windows 2000中，DVD播放器只在基于硬件的[[MPEG|MPEG]][[解码器|解码器]]存在时播放DVD。在Windows Me中，DVD播放器支持基于软件的MPEG解码器。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd316361.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396|title=Windows Media Player, Run DVD, Find the IP Address|accessdate=|date=5 January 2000|last=|first=|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|website=Ask the Windows 2000 Dev Team|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220031620/https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd316361.aspx?f=255&MSPPError=-2147217396}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/kb/272985|title=Description of DVD Player in Windows Millennium Edition|accessdate=|date=19 June 2014|last=|first=|publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|website=Support|edition=2.0|archive-date=2015-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150710211326/https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/kb/272985}}</ref>

在Windows XP、Vista、Windows 7和Windows 8中：DVDPlay.exe不再作为一个独立的应用程序，DVD功能被引入到Windows Media Player。虽然DVDPlay的可执行文件仍然存留在%Windir%\system32目录，但它只是执行Windows Media Player。不过，基于硬件的全功能版本在[[Windows_XP|Windows XP pre-RC1]]时仍存在。在Windows 8中， Windows Media Center和DVD播放支持被归入一个Windows 8 ''Pro''的付费使用的可选组件，以此应对解码器授权费用和越来越多不包括[[光驱|光驱]]的设备。<ref name="droppingDVD">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2403983,00.asp|title=Microsoft Dropping DVD Playback Support in Windows 8|accessdate=May 20, 2012|date=May 4, 2012|last=Albanesius|first=Chloe|work=[[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|archive-date=2012-05-07|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67UalgjiK?url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2403983,00.asp}}</ref>

== Windows 10版本 ==
'''Windows DVD播放器'''是一个[[Metro-style_apps|Windows商店应用]]，它可以为[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]提供DVD播放功能。<ref name="pcw-dvdplayer">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2953724/windows/how-to-play-dvds-in-windows-10-for-free.html|title=How to play DVDs in Windows 10 for free|accessdate=|date=29 July 2015|last=Paul|first=Ian|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|IDG]]|website=[[PCWorld|PCWorld]]|archive-date=2019-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190124112046/https://www.pcworld.com/article/2953724/windows/how-to-play-dvds-in-windows-10-for-free.html}}</ref>

在该应用启动时，它会搜索光盘驱动器上的影片文件以启动。它也可以作为一个光盘插入时的“自动播放”选项被使用。但是，如果应用运行时光盘被切换，该应用需要被重新启动。<ref name="pcw-dvdplayer">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2953724/windows/how-to-play-dvds-in-windows-10-for-free.html|title=How to play DVDs in Windows 10 for free|accessdate=|date=29 July 2015|last=Paul|first=Ian|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|IDG]]|website=[[PCWorld|PCWorld]]}}</ref>

它是作为一个付费应用提供，可在[[Windows商店|Windows商店]]中购买。Windows DVD播放器会免费分发给从包含Windows Media Center的[[Windows_7|Windows 7]]或[[Windows_8|Windows 8]]升级的用户，因为该软件已从Windows 10中去除。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.neowin.net/news/microsoft-rolls-out-windows-dvd-player-for-windows-10-users-who-used-to-have-media-center|title=Microsoft rolls out Windows DVD Player for Windows 10 users who used to have Media Center|accessdate=|date=29 July 2015|last=Weir|first=Andy|publisher=Neowin LLC|website=[[Neowin|Neowin]]|archive-date=2015-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150730172131/http://www.neowin.net/news/microsoft-rolls-out-windows-dvd-player-for-windows-10-users-who-used-to-have-media-center}}</ref><ref name="pcw-dvdplayer">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2953724/windows/how-to-play-dvds-in-windows-10-for-free.html|title=How to play DVDs in Windows 10 for free|accessdate=|date=29 July 2015|last=Paul|first=Ian|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|IDG]]|website=[[PCWorld|PCWorld]]}}</ref>

